        {
            "title": "美股早盤上揚 亞馬遜亮眼業績和蘋果的強勁預期提振風險偏好",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"607\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/J6erpIgaWnhVtAwhEGXGJA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/fd9670ccccc3c98305634f34dd27c55c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 受亞馬遜公司的亮眼業績以及蘋果公司強勁的假日季預期提振風險偏好影響，美國股市周五上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至紐約時間上午9:44，標普500指數上漲0.5%。該基準指數自4月份低點以來飆升近40%，邁向連續第六個月走高。以科技股為主的那斯達克100指數周五上漲1%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">亞馬遜股價飆升，因其雲業務錄得近三年來最強勁的增速。蘋果在發布新款iPhone後預計假日季銷售將出現跳升，這有助於讓投資者相信其旗艦產品仍是成長引擎。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d8da473d-0e75-37c1-9e1f-a5b26546aa3e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"607\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7tveINNX8y.Fu6jk85iLEA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/309f1d34fbbf07f8dc84c580de141971\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貿易方面的積極進展也提振了投資者信心。美國總統唐納德·川普在與中國國家主席習近平會面後稱，美中已在中國稀土供應問題上「解決」了分歧。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管關稅談判和科技企業財報傳遞樂觀信號，但在聯儲會本周早些時候對進一步降息的前景表示保留、且由於政府停擺美國進入數據空白期之後，投資者仍面臨前景不明的經濟環境。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">堪薩斯城聯儲行長Jeff Schmid表示，他在本周對降息投下反對票的原因是擔心經濟成長和投資會對通膨構成上行壓力。達拉斯聯邦儲備銀行行長Lorie Logan也表示，她不支持聯儲會本周降息的決定，並且由於通膨仍然過高，她很可能認為在下次會議上維持利率不變是合適的。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題S&amp;P 500 Jumps as Strong Amazon, Apple Scorecards Reignite Rally</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Julien Ponthus、Bernard Goyder、Neil Campling.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
